rich characters, captivating story.

1104
01:09:03,288 --> 01:09:05,707
I can see Bryan Alonsio in the lead

1105
01:09:05,708 --> 01:09:07,269
with Amy Ann Smith.

1106
01:09:07,270 --> 01:09:08,103
It's great.

1107
01:09:08,104 --> 01:09:09,350
It's just not for me.

1108
01:09:09,351 --> 01:09:10,352
What?

1109
01:09:10,353 --> 01:09:11,849
