and you could hold me like you used to

1156
01:11:36,550 --> 01:11:37,957
and I could, um.

1157
01:11:42,371 --> 01:11:44,493
Oops, drunk.

1158
01:11:45,830 --> 01:11:48,056
So, just call me back

1159
01:11:48,057 --> 01:11:51,163
