1160
01:11:58,466 --> 01:12:00,770
Every morning by the deserted hotel,

1161
01:12:00,771 --> 01:12:01,833
I'll be waiting.

1162
01:12:06,691 --> 01:12:08,941
I'm gonna live to be 110,

1163
01:12:10,090 --> 01:12:12,603
They tell me they'll extract my DNA.

