to waste your life on
something that never happens.

1229
01:16:30,091 --> 01:16:33,859
All I ever wanted was to tell my stories

1230
01:16:33,860 --> 01:16:36,939
and have someone say it's a great movie,

1231
01:16:36,940 --> 01:16:39,203
let's make it.

1232
01:16:39,204 --> 01:16:41,289
Don't give up, it can still happen.

1233
01:16:41,290 --> 01:16:45,209
No, no more dreams.

1234
01:16:45,210 --> 01:16:48,369
You know, the thing about dreams is

1235
01:16:48,370 --> 01:16:51,903
