1264
01:18:09,210 --> 01:18:11,289
Hey, it's a first.

1265
01:18:11,290 --> 01:18:13,040
I think I'd be really good at it.

1266
01:18:14,860 --> 01:18:17,439
Look, what are you doing right now?

1267
01:18:17,440 --> 01:18:19,049
I wanna hear about your movie.

1268
01:18:19,050 --> 01:18:20,150
Wanna go have a drink?

1269
01:18:21,150 --> 01:18:22,150
Seriously?

1270
01:18:22,930 --> 01:18:24,558
It's on me.

1271
01:18:24,559 --> 01:18:25,949
- Okay.
- Yeah?

1272
01:18:25,950 --> 01:18:26,809
Sure.

1273
01:18:26,809 --> 01:18:27,809
All right.

1274
01:18:28,840 --> 01:18:30,759
You really wanna hear about my script.

1275
01:18:30,760 --> 01:18:31,909
Yeah.

1276
01:18:31,910 --> 01:18:33,199
- Okay, let's do it.
- Let's go.

1277
01:18:33,200 --> 01:18:34,766
You gotta read this book, though.

1278
01:18:34,767 --> 01:18:35,808
I'm kidding.

