1284
01:19:02,760 --> 01:19:04,039
I paid for love.

1285
01:19:04,040 --> 01:19:05,343
I paid.

1286
01:19:05,344 --> 01:19:07,840
I figured big guy, big love.

1287
01:19:07,841 --> 01:19:11,232
Hola.

1288
01:19:11,233 --> 01:19:13,514
Gracias, mi amor.

1289
01:19:29,077 --> 01:19:30,077
Oh, hey.

1290
01:19:45,950 --> 01:19:47,477
I'm glad you're happy.

1291
01:19:49,057 --> 01:19:50,596
I'm very happy, look.

1292
01:19:50,597 --> 01:19:52,259
You look happy.

1293
01:19:52,260 --> 01:19:53,349
So you paid for him?

1294
01:19:53,350 --> 01:19:54,619
Yeah, I did.

1295
01:19:54,620 --> 01:19:56,689
It was amazing, don't make
fun of me, I loved it.

1296
01:19:56,690 --> 01:19:58,097
Because I created something

1297
