1344
01:22:59,559 --> 01:23:00,393
No, no, you didn't.

1345
01:23:00,394 --> 01:23:02,409
You didn't even try.

1346
01:23:02,410 --> 01:23:03,243
I did try.

1347
01:23:03,244 --> 01:23:04,609
No, you didn't.

1348
