1350
01:23:08,809 --> 01:23:10,009
You could have tried harder.

1351
01:23:16,950 --> 01:23:21,063
I pictured you every
day coming to surprise me.

1352
01:23:22,660 --> 01:23:24,923
I woke up every morning
with a broken heart.

